snippet: Representative Joe Walsh, a Tea Party Republican from Illinois, seems to think that by belittling the sacrifice of Tammy Duckworth, who served and was injured in Iraq, he can win re-election.
abstract: Editorial condemns Illinois Republican Rep Joe Walsh for belittling the military service of his Democratic opponent Tammy Duckworth.
lead_paragraph: Representative Joe Walsh, a Tea Party Republican from Illinois, seems to think that by belittling the sacrifice of Tammy Duckworth, who served and was injured in Iraq, he can win re-election.
